description: Best practices for async HTTP requests with Hyper
globs: **/*.rs
---

- Use `hyper::Client` for making HTTP requests
- Implement custom headers and authentication with `hyper::header`
- Use `hyper::Body` for streaming request/response bodies
- Implement timeouts with `hyper::client::connect::HttpConnector`
- Use `hyper::server::conn::Http` for creating HTTP servers